7 SECTION 3. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Department of
8 Justice the sum of fifty thousand dollars ($50,000) in recurring funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal
9 year to be allocated to the Office of the Attorney General to enforce the provisions of Article 43
10 of Chapter 66 of the General Statutes, as amended by this act.
11 SECTION 4. Sections 1 and 2 of this act become effective October 1, 2025, and
12 apply to service agreements entered into on or after that date. Section 3 of this act becomes
13 effective July 1, 2025. The remainder of this act is effective when it becomes law.
